Metadata in a table <p><pre><code>template = """
&lt;style&gt;
    .container {
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        font-family: sans-serif;
    }
    .row {
        display: flex;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    .row:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
    }
    .column {
        flex: 1;
        padding: 8px;
    }
    .column:first-child {
        border-right: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
&lt;/style&gt;
&lt;div class="container"&gt;
    &lt;div class="header"&gt;
        &lt;div class="column"&gt;Metadata&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="column"&gt;Value&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    {{#each record.metadata}}
    &lt;div class="row"&gt;
        &lt;div class="column"&gt;{{@key}}&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="column"&gt;{{this}}&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    {{/each}}
&lt;/div&gt;
"""
record = rg.Record(
    fields={"text": "hello"},
    metadata={
        "name": "John Doe",
        "age": 25,
    }
)
</code></pre> </p> JSON/Code viewer <pre><code>import argilla as rg
</code></pre>
